HEADWORD: Hemiopsia
<hw>Hem`i*op"si*a</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/ half + Gr.
<?/ sight.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A defect of vision in
